{"tid":296760,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[震驚有片］方大同撼贏林宥嘉成為第三位港男歌手奪台灣金曲歌王","createTime":"2017-06-25T00:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T23:50:09.000Z","uid":28422,"like":57,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9935197122bca33059ef699ccf40a85c4ba2aab","tid":296760,"uid":28422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T00:54:07.000Z","msg":"在2017年以前，僅僅得張學友（1998）同單丸迅（2003、2015）兩位拎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n方大同在尋晚正式成為第三位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/r9vF5ItCdNo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fr9vF5ItCdNo&d=fZFS8tXsTIlra8mgLvL2fL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=cd8485ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/r9vF5ItCdNo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果：草東沒有派對暴衝大贏 方大同 艾怡良首奪歌王歌后<br />\nVideo: <a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/entertainment/20170625/37694746/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Fappledaily%2Farticle%2Fentertainment%2F20170625%2F37694746%2F&d=fZFS8tXsTIlra8mgLvL2fL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=4b0b72d3\" target=\"_blank\">m.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/entertainment/20170625/37694746/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/085002_396b38f94026cdf3c3da554a22518dfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F085002_396b38f94026cdf3c3da554a22518dfe.jpg&h=6bf42aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【李志展╱台北報導】第28屆金曲獎得主昨晚揭曉，香港歌手方大同擊敗新婚的林宥嘉與二度當爸的周杰倫（周董）等勁敵，首度登基歌王寶座。他熬了10年、5度摃龜，昨終於獲獎，語帶哽咽：「特別感謝我的母親一直支持我。」最佳女歌手獎落艾怡良，成軍20年的五月天拿下大獎「最佳國語專輯」，貝斯手瑪莎感性致辭，最後團員抱在一起，場面感人。獨立新團「草東沒有派對」拿下3獎，與桑布伊、秦四風並列大贏家。<br />\n<br />\n方大同以《JTW西遊記》第6度叩關金曲，過去他每發片必入圍，卻總在最高得獎呼聲中落榜，今年領獎前特別和男歌手、女歌手入圍者擊掌，果真集到好運。<br />\n金曲評審團主席黃韻玲表示，複審有20位評審，投票過半才能決定得獎人，歌王戰無懸念，方大同首輪便以18票壓倒性勝出。黃韻玲轉述方大同得獎理由：「創作豐富，音樂有企圖心，巧妙將中文與R&amp;B結合，非常自然。」有評審認為林宥嘉聲音辨識度高，退伍後作品成熟，但未化成選票，第3度落馬。"},{"pid":"fb914282e0e84efc265a305c8b19607ffb975014","tid":296760,"uid":14274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T00:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a96e84007717ec87788734447338f6cd7e1c568","tid":296760,"uid":73883,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T00:56:54.000Z","msg":"佢的確係有料，去台灣發展係好事，留喺香港只會嘥左佢嘅才華。"},{"pid":"c788f7181b0778dc9d0cfdbd63fda5ce404e98ba","tid":296760,"uid":43918,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T00:58:35.000Z","msg":"香港人都係繼續聽罐頭k歌啦<br />\nWe dont deserve Khalil Fong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1395867790f9f879c0129ece188f70ab0b98725b","tid":296760,"uid":3195,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:00:53.000Z","msg":"兩個都好鍾意，<br />\n但可能有考慮到林宥嘉仲會繼續玩落去，<br />\n而方大同唔會（？！）<br />\n不過兩個都係好比心機做音樂嘅歌手，<br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd7acb42ab4983345dd8385a814747b41cb8fa1","tid":296760,"uid":70946,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:04:53.000Z","msg":"方大同：唱廣東歌冇前途"},{"pid":"dad62049181efb7964da6f6d9e3c83f7d395cec4","tid":296760,"uid":28422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:07:53.000Z","msg":"邊個偷偷放下負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a46f8615307f714297e16490d4402922958bb0","tid":296760,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:10:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2de606e66768f23551239e7060551bc07f87d354","tid":296760,"uid":21028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:16:32.000Z","msg":"睇到台灣既競爭程度同香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係...."},{"pid":"601b713de270e744145d4fe018387768f127b801","tid":296760,"uid":1482,